  <strong><a name="howmuch"></a>How much does is cost to post a job Ad on jobbslist?</strong><br /><br />
  $49 for each job post (pricing subject to change).<br /><br />
  <strong><a name="howlong"></a>How long does a job post will be published for?</strong><br /><br />
  30 days from the day it was published.<br /><br />
  <strong><a name="howpost"></a>How do I post a Job Ad?</strong><br /><br />
  Posting a job ad is super simple. Follow these simple steps:<br /><br />
  <ol>
    <li>http://www.jobbslist.com/new</li>
    <li>Enter all information regarding job posting.</li>
    <li>Click the Preview Ad Button</li>
    <li>If you are satisfied with the job posting, then you are ready to publish your Ad</li>
    <li>Enter billing information, then click publish.</li>
    <li>You're all done! Your job posting will be automatically published for 30 days.</li>
  </ol>
<br />
