<strong><a name="repost"></a>How do I repost my job ad after 30 days?</strong><br /><br />
The same process as creating a "new" job ad.<br /><br />
<a href="http://www.jobbslist.com/new">www.jobbslist.com/new</a><br /><br /><br />
<strong><a name="multiple"></a>Can I post multiple jobs on one job posting?</strong><br /><br />
No. Multiple jobs on a single job posting will be deleted and are non-refundable.<br /><br />
